---

This project bundles a vector database derived from publicly-available
Lauterbach TRACE32 documentation. The PDFs themselves remain copyright
Lauterbach Datentechnik GmbH. The embeddings and chunked text excerpts are
included only as a search index; for the full primary source see
https://www.lauterbach.com.

This project does not vendor Lauterbach's licensed `t32api` Python wrapper
or shared library. Those are loaded dynamically from the user's own TRACE32
installation at runtime.
